text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r04_quatrain r05_s r06_phr r07_line

LMNL.text: Some fowls there be that have so perfect sight

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r04_quatrain r05_s r06_phr
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r04_quatrain r05_s r06_phr r08_line

LMNL.text: Again the sun their eyes for to defend;

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r04_quatrain r05_s
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r04_quatrain r05_s r09_phr r10_line

LMNL.text: And some because the light doth them offend

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r04_quatrain r05_s r09_phr
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r04_quatrain r05_s r09_phr r11_line

LMNL.text: Do never 'pear but in the dark or night.

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain r13_s r14_phr r15_line

LMNL.text: Other rejoice that see the fire bright

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain r13_s r14_phr
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain r13_s r14_phr r16_line

LMNL.text: And ween to play in it,

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain r13_s r16_line
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain r13_s r16_line r17_phr
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain r13_s
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain r13_s r18_line r19_phr

LMNL.text: And find the contrary of it that they intend.

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain r20_s r21_line r22_phr
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain r20_s r21_line
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r03_octave r12_quatrain r20_s r21_line r23_phr

LMNL.text: of that sort I may be by right,

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r20_s
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r20_s r24_sestet r25_quatrain r26_phr r27_line

LMNL.text: For to withstand her look I am not able

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r20_s r24_sestet r25_quatrain r26_phr
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r20_s r24_sestet r25_quatrain r26_phr r28_line

LMNL.text: And yet can I not hide me in no dark place,

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r20_s r24_sestet r25_quatrain
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r20_s r24_sestet r25_quatrain r29_line r30_phr

LMNL.text: Remembrance so followeth me of that face.

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r24_sestet r25_quatrain
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r24_sestet r25_quatrain r31_s r32_line r33_phr
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r24_sestet r25_quatrain r31_s r32_line
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r24_sestet r25_quatrain r31_s r32_line r34_phr
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r24_sestet r31_s
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r24_sestet r31_s r35_couplet r36_line r37_phr

LMNL.text: My destiny to behold her doth me lead,

text.cf: r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r24_sestet r31_s r35_couplet
r01_sonneteer r02_sonnet r24_sestet r31_s r35_couplet r38_line r39_phr

LMNL.text: Yet do I know I run into the gleed.
